  "data": {
    "description": "<p>You may only target allies with this skill. Use when the target performs a [Weapon Attack], [Magic Attack], or [Special Attack] on an enemy with the [Boss] or [Raid] tag. The [Hate] cost of that action is reduced by -1 (minimum 0). This skill can only be used during the round it is used once, even if the number of uses is exhausted.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A special skill that encourages allies by playing a musical accompaniment to pray for good luck. A blow delivered along with this tone becomes a part of the Shinto ritual, making it less likely to arouse animosity.</p>",
